paragraph is a series of related sentences developing a central idea, called the 
 <span style=" color: red">topic.</span>
 Try to think about paragraphs in terms of thematic unity: a paragraph is a sentence or a group of sentences that supports one 
 <span style=" color: red"> central, unified idea.</span>
